question: Rachel had to complete 7 pages of math homework. If she had to complete 4 more pages of math homework than reading homework. How many pages of reading homework did she have to complete?
response:
Rachel had to complete 7 pages of math homework. If she had to complete 4 more pages of math homework than reading homework, it means she had to complete 7 + 4 = 11 pages of reading homework.
The answer is 11.
